## Daily Usage (Employee Instructions)

1. Double-click **`start_system.bat`** in the project folder.
2. Three things start automatically:
   - ✅ XAMPP Apache + MySQL
   - ✅ ZKTeco Bridge (in its own window)
   - ✅ Ngrok tunnel (shows the public URL)
3. Tell the Boss: **"System is ready."**

The Boss opens their **bookmarked ngrok URL** from home — it never changes.

